      <title>Crocs 股价因 Sydney Sweeney 协议升级而延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/crocs-shares-extend-gain-after-sydney-sweeney-pact-spurs-upgrade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于华尔街认为与女演员西德尼·斯威尼 (Sydney Sweeney) 的合作将刺激市场对 Crocs Inc. Heydude 系列鞋的需求，该公司股价因此获得提振。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/crocs-shares-extend-gain-after-sydney-sweeney-pact-spurs-upgrade</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 17:27:51 GMT</pubDate>
