    <item>
      <title>由于囚犯减少，监狱运营商放弃了市政资助的拘留中心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/jail-operator-drops-muni-funded-detention-center-on-less-inmates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚利桑那州一家拘留中心的运营者表示，尽管该中心关押的囚犯人数有所下降，但维持该设施运营的成本已经过高，难以承受。该中心未偿还的市政债务约为 2470 万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/jail-operator-drops-muni-funded-detention-center-on-less-inmates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 16:04:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杰克逊霍尔会议召开前，巴西雷亚尔和墨西哥比索领跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/em-investors-await-fresh-signals-from-powell-at-jackson-hole</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元和美国国债收益率上涨，新兴市场货币指数周四出现一个月来最大盘中跌幅，交易员们正在等待美联储主席杰罗姆鲍威尔明天在杰克逊霍尔的讲话。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/em-investors-await-fresh-signals-from-powell-at-jackson-hole</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 10:18:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大铁路公司拒绝工会工人上班，贸易陷入混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/canada-railways-lock-out-workers-as-talks-fail-snarling-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大两条最大的铁路公司于周四凌晨在与工会领导人的谈判失败后关闭，立即阻断了北美供应链的主干道，这些供应链每天的贸易额约为 10 亿加元（7.4 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-22/canada-railways-lock-out-workers-as-talks-fail-snarling-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 04:35:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
